==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tunnel stern
<hw>Tun"nel stern</hw>. <def>A design of motor-boat stern, for use in
shallow waters, in which the propeller is housed in a tunnel and does
not extend below the greatest draft.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tunny</ent>⟦br⟧
